   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project goal is to initiate legislation and action to combat the causes and effects of climate change in Ha Giang Province. Local ethnic minority communities will pilot a participatory community-based flood and land-slide control and prevention model.  Households, especially the poor in the resettlement from flash-floods and land-slide danger areas will develop more resilient livelihood activities to adapt to climate change. Ha Giang Province&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s leaders and key agencies including Committee of Floods and Storm Control, Department of Planning and Investment and Department of Environment, Natural Resources will be supported in developing their Action Plan of climate change adaptation and mitigation.</narrative>
  </description>
